---
title: Garlic & Herb-Crumbed Pork with Garden Salad, Potato Wedges & Herby Mayo
description: Everyone is going to want a bite of this dish at dinner. It’s hard enough to resist a panko-crumbed, golden pork let alone when you add delicious garlic and herb flavours into the crumb itself so it cooks into the pork. Then there’s the wedges and dill-parsley mayo for dipping that makes mouths water. This is going to be too hard to resist, best to dig in!
